{"tid":1138632,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[盃賽最頂上一戰]苟芸慧 對 陳法拉 18-19 LIHKG香港女神總會盃決賽","createTime":"2019-05-04T16:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T01:47:00.000Z","uid":92376,"like":130,"dislike":96,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9c8dcde2259bd8572eb363c80a0b1721f251f02c","tid":1138632,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"以下為馬上舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可直接以正負評功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(超)苟芸慧vs陳法拉(超)<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-19 LIHKG香港女神總會盃決賽</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2019-5-5 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/mGrYA4t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmGrYA4t.png&h=f45dbe55&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/bSWW1Hu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbSWW1Hu.png&h=28e7f4c6&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(超5)苟芸慧vs陳法拉(超2)</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/XTGGwlB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXTGGwlB.png&h=4d2abbaa&s={SIZE}\" />joyfulck falachenfala<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/XTGGwlB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXTGGwlB.png&h=4d2abbaa&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以正負評功能(前正後負)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的正負評功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽決賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"d01f762779244316986f1